high_descs: Turn to the left, Head to the kitchen table
Take the lettuce from the table
Turn around, head to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the lettuce in the fridge
Wait 7 seconds, open the fridge, take the lettuce out of the fridge, close the fridge
Turn around, head to the trash, put the lettuce in the trash
anns.task_desc: Put the lettuce in the fridge for 7 seconds, throw the lettuce in the trash

high_descs: turn left and walk over to the left side of the kitchen table on your right
grab the lettuce off of the table there
turn left and walk to the end of the room, then turn left to walk to the fridge up ahead
place the lettuce down inside of the fridge there, let it cool then take it back out
turn around and walk forwards a bit to the garbage bin that's on your left
place the lettuce down inside of the garbage bin on the left side
anns.task_desc: place cooled lettuce inside of the garbage bin

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the table that's on your right and then turn right to face it once you get to the left side.
Pick up the head of lettuce that's near the yellow handled knife.
Turn left and walk to the door then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and then chill the lettuce in the fridge on the middle shelf then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the garbage in the left corner in front of you.
Put the head of lettuce in the garbage.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in the garbage.
